          <div class="pillar-card"><div class="pillar-num">02</div><h3>Scalability</h3><p>Works at the scale clinics actually need.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-card"><div class="pillar-num">03</div><h3>Sustainability</h3><p>Economically and operationally viable long-term.</p></div>
          <div class="pillar-card"><div class="pillar-num">04</div><h3>Patient Value</h3><p>Measurably improves outcomes or access.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div></section>

